    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your hive immediately swarms to your protection covering your body in a cloak of defensive bees. You gain 18 temporary hit points until the beginning of your turn. If a creature hits you with a melee attack while you have these hit points, once per turn must make a Constitution saving throw, gaining a rank of Envenomed on a failed save.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase temporary hit points gained by +8. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank, increase the ranks of Envenomed inflicted to +2. At S-Rank, increase the ranks of Envenomed inflicted to +3.</p>",
